     Let me[0m[2m identify the root causes[0m[2m:
     
     **Issue[0m[2m 1 -[0m[2m Duplicate[0m[2m Processing[0m[2m ([0m[2mjob_queue.py:[0m[2mde[0m[2mqueue)**[0m[2m:
